                <ul>
                    <li><strong><?php _e('Complete PHPUnit test coverage (#1774)', 'tc-data-tables'); ?></strong> — <?php _e('TC_Validation_Service::validate() and sanitize_rules() (added in #1742, v6.3.8) were exercised only by the legacy custom test runner. The PHPUnit main suite now covers all 11 methods and 144 lines of the class. No user-facing changes.', 'tc-data-tables'); ?></li>
                </ul>

                <h3><?php _e('v7.0.1 — Parallel test execution (Paratest)', 'tc-data-tables'); ?></h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong><?php _e('Paratest parallel PHPUnit (#1771)', 'tc-data-tables'); ?></strong> — <?php _e('Full PHPUnit suite now completes in ≈2 minutes instead of ≈17 minutes. The shim suite (592 legacy test-issue files) runs via paratest in --functional mode, parallelising the previously serial @runInSeparateProcess subprocesses across 10 worker processes. The main suite runs concurrently as a background process. Use tools/test-all-suites.sh for the unified gate.', 'tc-data-tables'); ?></li>
                </ul>

