                <ul>
                    <li><strong><?php _e('Bulk Column Fill (Pro)', 'tc-data-tables'); ?></strong> — <?php _e('Select one or more rows, then click the new "Fill Column" button in the toolbar. A modal lets you choose a column and enter a value; clicking Apply writes that value to the chosen field for every selected entry. Pro-gated with server-side capability enforcement. The button hides itself when no rows are checked (#1745).', 'tc-data-tables'); ?></li>
