                <h3><?php _e('v6.4.3 — Column Picker Toolbar Selector Fix', 'tc-data-tables'); ?></h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong><?php _e('Fix: picker button not appearing', 'tc-data-tables'); ?></strong> — <?php _e('initColumnPicker() searched for .gt-toolbar but the actual frontend toolbar element is .gt-table-controls. Button now renders correctly after enabling the picker in Display Options.', 'tc-data-tables'); ?></li>
