                    <li><strong>4.82.0</strong> — <?php _e('Audit close (CLOSES #793 — umbrella): GF field-type support audit complete. Filed 4 final children for residual render gaps (#817 name, #818 time, #819 fileupload, #820 consent) and marked the entire Add-on section in docs/developer/field-type-support.md as deferred-to-per-add-on-ticket (those can only be audited after the owning add-on is installed). Cumulative across all slices: 14 children filed (10 closed + 4 open for follow-up), 13 minor releases (v4.69.0-v4.81.0), ~1000 new test assertions. The matrix doc is the source-of-truth for what Gravity Tables supports per field type. **No runtime change in this release** — closes the umbrella tracking ticket.', 'tc-data-tables'); ?></li>
