                    <li><strong>4.35.0</strong> — <?php _e('Feature (slice 3b — first customer-facing Airtable slice): Airtable settings admin page (#517). New "Airtable" submenu under Advanced Tables. Three admin-post handlers (save / test connection / clear) verify nonce + manage_options and delegate to the slice-3a credential service and slice-2 sync engine. Test connection uses page_size=1 — cheapest probe that verifies auth. View pre-fills base + table from storage but NEVER pre-fills the token (mask-on-display). Inline notices surface success / failure with the sync engine\'s actual error message. Retires the slice-1 + slice-2 + slice-3a orphan invariants in this same PR (4-way retirement). 31 new assertions plus inversion of 4 prior ACs; 411/411 plugin tests pass. **Customer-facing**: customers can now configure Airtable connectivity entirely from wp-admin. Slice 4+ tackles two-way sync (#613).', 'tc-data-tables'); ?></li>
