                    <li><strong>4.24.0</strong> — <?php _e('Feature (slice 4 of N): Per-row post_webhook built-in action (#618). Mirrors slice 3 send_email pattern. New helper register_builtin_post_webhook + filter gt_post_webhook_enabled. Handler gt_handle_post_webhook_action verifies nonce + edit_posts, loads entry, reads URL from gt_post_webhook_url filter, POSTs JSON via wp_remote_post (15s timeout). Default payload: {event, action, table_id, row_id, entry}. Customization filter gt_post_webhook_payload. Redirects with gt_webhook_sent flag. 20 new assertions; slice-3 AC#6 retired. 327/327 tests pass. Slice 5 owes per-table admin UI for templates.', 'tc-data-tables'); ?></li>
