                    <li><strong>4.15.0</strong> — <?php _e('Maintainer feature: Phase 3 loop-driven coverage gate (#671). Ships tools/coverage-gate.sh + tools/coverage-gate.php + tools/coverage-allowlist.txt. Gate runs as part of LOOP_STRATEGY.md step [8] before the loop merges its own PR: parses build/coverage/clover.xml against docs/COVERAGE_BASELINE.md, reports regressions and improvements, exits non-zero if any file drops below baseline. PHP helpers exposed for testability: gt_gate_parse_clover, gt_gate_parse_baseline, gt_gate_compute_delta. Skip-mode: when clover.xml is missing/empty (no pcov yet) or baseline holds no numeric rows, the gate exits 0 — keeps loop green until real data flows. Allowlist format enforces `# justification` per entry. The 100% coverage initiative\'s infrastructure layer is now complete (#668 → #670 → #679 → #682 → #669 → #671); only pcov install + #672 JS surface remain. 26 new test assertions; 318/318 plugin tests pass. No GitHub Actions involvement. No customer-facing change.', 'tc-data-tables'); ?></li>
